title: NFL Around the League: NFC North - August 26th, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: NFC North - August 26th, 2013
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling, give you the latest news from around the league before focusing on a breakdown of the NFC North. Find out how to win a box of cereal straight from Studio 66. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
